docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: Two of the five obstetricians on Aquidneck Island are turning away pregnant women on welfare who come to them for prenatal care, and the three other obstetricians here say they will shut their doors in the next few days in a dispute over the Medicaid fee paid by the state.

headline.main: DOCTORS, IN RHODE ISLAND FEE PROTEST, REFUSE POOR PATIENTS
